Sales Data Analysis - SQL & Python
This project uses SQL queries and Python libraries to analyze sales data and provide various visualizations.

ğŸ“ Content
SQL Queries:

Maximum, minimum, and total sales analysis by store
Comparison of average sales on holiday and non-holiday days
Time series analysis (sales totals by year and month)
Missing data detection and data cleaning operations
Python Analysis and Visualization:

Graphical analysis of sales data using Seaborn and Matplotlib
Bar charts showing maximum sales
Graphs comparing holiday days with non-holiday days
Line chart analysis of time series data
ğŸ“Š Technologies Used
Database: Microsoft SQL Server
Python Libraries: Pandas, NumPy, Seaborn, Matplotlib, Pyodbc
